  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Looper Tactics is a captivating strategy card-based RPG,  blending elements of deck-building games, classic card battles, and auto-battler. You will traverse a board-style map, continuously assembling and strengthening your deck through battles, events, and treasure hunts — all while uncovering the truth hidden in this fantastical world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/2091a3385eb2d2a912e88664ddd7c22d.poster.avif?t=1770715547\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/2091a3385eb2d2a912e88664ddd7c22d.webm?t=1770715547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/2091a3385eb2d2a912e88664ddd7c22d.mp4?t=1770715547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/3ce48eff6e0b2e8a5dfa7c74e2a17237.avif?t=1770715547\" width=620 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your journey in Looper Tactics, you’re free to explore the map however you like. Advance or retreat. Decide which tiles to explore next and get ready before engaging in the ultimate battle that awaits you on each level! How you progress in the game is your mere decision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/f4848d52a80e4ce3446c4d06731d49e2.poster.avif?t=1770715547\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/f4848d52a80e4ce3446c4d06731d49e2.webm?t=1770715547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/f4848d52a80e4ce3446c4d06731d49e2.mp4?t=1770715547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just remember, as you advance on the map, the enemies will get stronger, but you’ll also encounter new allies and creatures to enhance your deck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/ac69e14b607981facc29ad480b60ca2f.avif?t=1770715547\" width=620 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a deck-building card game, Looper Tactics gameplay is inspired by Hearthstone, Artifact, and Hearthstone Battlegrounds’ mechanics, all while adding strategic and roguelite elements. In the game, you collect resources through battles, events, and treasure hunts, strengthening your deck in preparation for the ultimate boss challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/32fde3672608339ba26e51bd50aa4e58.poster.avif?t=1770715547\" width=598 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/32fde3672608339ba26e51bd50aa4e58.webm?t=1770715547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/32fde3672608339ba26e51bd50aa4e58.mp4?t=1770715547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/7e64f690fac0afedaf9a68af08195c13.avif?t=1770715547\" width=620 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minions belong to different races -  Demons, Elves, Mechs, Elementals and Dragons - and have two distinct forms to choose from.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/162c25b22f42dd0c01e14cef5e7e6372.avif?t=1770715547\" width=600 height=252 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each race has unique mechanics and combining it with different units and spells can lead to multiple combat styles. Choose the one that suits your strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/2d88fe9984f4ee705b7e3460beb60e30.avif?t=1770715547\" width=600 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/8f3c242d613b4986b4a0878e99a14448.avif?t=1770715547\" width=620 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging in battles will allow you to enhance your minion’s attributes by using abilities, attacks or spells. These changes are permanent and will help you until the end of your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/cb85d699627edfa06064c2de9721efbc.poster.avif?t=1770715547\" width=602 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/cb85d699627edfa06064c2de9721efbc.webm?t=1770715547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/cb85d699627edfa06064c2de9721efbc.mp4?t=1770715547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan carefully as even the lowest-tier minion can become a formidable force after countless battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/59f66cf3cb6fefa0e5d24cd83dfab837.avif?t=1770715547\" width=620 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Confront every battle as a new opportunity. Your strategy during these auto-battle confrontations won’t only affect the current challenge but also future encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each movement is a new opportunity. Think of your next step as a fundamental part of your whole strategy, as different tiles will allow you to gain blessings, trade cards or engage in battles of increasing difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/0d1aa807ef4ce69ede9297f4c1753794.poster.avif?t=1770715547\" width=600 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/0d1aa807ef4ce69ede9297f4c1753794.webm?t=1770715547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/0d1aa807ef4ce69ede9297f4c1753794.mp4?t=1770715547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow stronger as your hero and companions' attributes improve based on your fighting style and choices on the map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/254c24912d5882615174a9600d943400.avif?t=1770715547\" width=620 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It all began when the ancient empire dared to play God. They constructed a whole world within a container, creating synthetic souls to inhabit it. But as they watched their creations grow, fear crept in. The only solution to prevent these creations from leading to the world’s ruin was to seal them away and keep them on an endless cycle of reincarnation. A fate the synthetic souls would endure for all eternity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The empire believed they had done enough, but as time passed, doubts began to arise. Would the cycle of reincarnation be enough to keep the world safe? Only time will tell…</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Looper Tactics is a captivating strategy card-based RPG,  blending elements of deck-building games, classic card battles, and auto-battler. You will traverse a board-style map, continuously assembling and strengthening your deck through battles, events, and treasure hunts — all while uncovering the truth hidden in this fantastical world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/2091a3385eb2d2a912e88664ddd7c22d.poster.avif?t=1770715547\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/2091a3385eb2d2a912e88664ddd7c22d.webm?t=1770715547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/2091a3385eb2d2a912e88664ddd7c22d.mp4?t=1770715547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/3ce48eff6e0b2e8a5dfa7c74e2a17237.avif?t=1770715547\" width=620 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your journey in Looper Tactics, you’re free to explore the map however you like. Advance or retreat. Decide which tiles to explore next and get ready before engaging in the ultimate battle that awaits you on each level! How you progress in the game is your mere decision.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140850/extras/f4848d52a80e4ce3446c4d06731d49e2.poster.avif?t=1770715547\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.aka